{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Specific Government Covid-19 secure guidance is required for Tanning Salons",
        "additional_details": "Currently, Tanning Salons are incorrectly classed as a close-contact service with respect to Covid-19 restrictions. Tanning Salons are entirely contact free, and have an almost uniquely maintained environment giving rise to enhanced ventilation of the entire premises.",
        "background": "The Government should be required to update its Covid-19 secure guidance, so that there is separate guidance for Tanning Salons, which recognises that this is not a close contact service, and that the guidance on close contact services does not refer to Tanning Salons.",
